com.basho.riak.client.api.commands.datatypes

Class SetUpdate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.basho.riak.client.api.commands.datatypes.SetUpdate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DatatypeUpdate

    public class SetUpdate
extends Object
implements DatatypeUpdate
    An update to a Riak set datatype.

    When building an UpdateSet or UpdateMap command this class is used to encapsulate the update to be performed on a Riak set datatype.

    Since:
    2.0
    Author:
    Dave Rusek
